com.buschmais.xo.spi.annotation

Annotation Type RelationDefinition


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=ANNOTATION_TYPE)
public @interface RelationDefinition
    Marks an annotation as relation definition, i.e. a type represents a relation if it is annotated with an annotation which itself is annotated byRelationDefinition.
